Here i took guess number as 10
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Scanner obj=new Scanner(System.in);
        int sum=0;
        System.out.println("whether the input is onside or outside of 10");
        do{
            int n=obj.nextInt();
            if(n==10){
            break;
            }
            else
                sum+=1;

        }while(true);
        System.out.println("it takes these many chance="+sum);

    }
}
Output:
1
2
10
it takes these many chance=2
